  "detailed_description": "Witness the birth of sapient AI in this sprawling atmospheric hacking adventure.<br><br>Combining traditional Metroidvania mechanics with a dynamic branching narrative system, <i><strong>Recompile</strong></i> challenges players to explore, fight, hack and survive. Discover the many secrets beneath the ancient digital landscape, and prepare for system-wide reconfiguration.<br><br>The game's entire narrative takes place within 1 second of real time.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/986310/extras/steam_page.gif?t=1554913642\" ><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traditional Metroidvania progression combined with a unique narrative branching system.<br></li><li>A range of futuristic weapons and super-powered abilities.<br></li><li>Intense and intelligent combat with a host of deadly NPCs and boss battles.<br></li><li>Hack through environmental circuitry, logic gates and even enemies.<br></li><li>Multiple endings depending on play style.<br></li><li>A variety of assist mode options to help with game accessibility.<br></li><li>Reactive soundtrack of blistering electro.</li></ul>",
